Luis's Ground Zero  

Ideally, Luis Suarez would have chosen a stadium other than the Etihad at which to make his return to playing in England. 

The Uruguayan appeared twice for Liverpool at City’s ground last season, failed to score in either game and picked up a booking. He certainly put that right.

