James hits the big time 

Manchester City will hope the inclusion of James Milner in the starting XI will be a sweetener for the England player, who is out of contract in the summer. 

Milner is worried about not playing enough big games this season but here he was for the biggest so far, ahead of Fernandinho and new £28million striker Wilfried Bony, with Yaya Toure suspended. 

